At the entrance, event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards, while healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is made over the PA system, and the dean stops by to thank recruiters for supporting the university.

Career counselors are present to redirect unsure students toward applicable industries and remind attendees to maintain eye contact. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. Finance firms offer QR codes for immediate internship applications, while human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system, and as the fair progresses, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, while a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session.
